88a6d2","tid":1074773,"uid":20696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"先半年就咁⋯⋯<br />\n咁唔好同居啦<br />\n<br />\n其實無方法，佢肯陪就會陪<br />\n唔肯陪嘅，好似你咁講，佢只係個人坐喺你隔離心不在焉。"},{"pid":"d908c2fbb5dd715169c147a7994e102cdcefd7bb","tid":1074773,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T18:58:44.000Z","msg":"冇另一半俾我陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3858472a30ebe423c300a76483c959db4e542d79","tid":1074773,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c5074443ddd836297d725e44c3294cc473510e","tid":1074773,"uid":218033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6a2149853ab8fae718eb2b425f0ca87d9176b92","tid":1074773,"uid":81424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"打埋一份囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:10:56.000Z","msg":"本身打機唔叻，佢會嫌我廢燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T23:56:37.000Z","msg":"廢咪練囉<br />\n冇共同興趣好難維繫感情"}]}